                                "issuer":  "TCEL",
                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: BI-022 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "BI-001 Registered source required | Preventive | Reject unregistered source ingestion | Critical | Data Governance. BI-002 Source schema validation | Preventive | Quarantine on mismatch | Critical | Data Governance. BI-003 Duplicate ingestion prevention | Preventive | Idempotent reject | Critical | Platform. BI-004 Immutable raw archive | Evidence | Block mutation of raw layer | Critical | Data Governance. BI-005 Certified data product approval | Governance | Block publication until certified | Critical | Data Governance. BI-006 Metric owner required | Preventive | Reject metric without owner | High | Data Governance. BI-007 Metric formula and source required | Evidence | Reject undocumented metric | Critical | Data Governance. BI-008 KPI certification required | Governance | Block uncertified KPI use in dashboards | Critical | Data Governance. BI-009 Certified/exploratory labeling | Preventive | Reject ambiguous presentation | Critical | BI Owner. BI-010 Tenant isolation | Preventive | Deny cross-tenant access | Critical | Security. BI-011 Row and column security | Preventive | Deny unauthorized field access | Critical | Security. BI-012 Restricted data masking | Preventive | Mask on unauthorized query | Critical | Security. BI-013 Lineage required | Evidence | Block certification without lineage | Critical | Data Governance. BI-014 Quality score required | Evidence | Restrict metric below threshold | High | Data Governance. BI-015 Stale source restriction | Preventive | Mark Data Restricted | Critical | Data Governance. BI-016 Reconciliation failure restriction | Preventive | Restrict affected metric | Critical | Data Governance. BI-017 Semantic model versioning | Evidence | Require version on change | High | Data Governance. BI-018 Breaking metric change approval | Governance | Require approval and notice | Critical | BI Owner. BI-019 Controlled report publication | Preventive | Require approval before external use | High | BI Owner. BI-020 Controlled export | Preventive | Require approval and watermark | High | Security. BI-021 AI source mutation prohibited | Preventive | Deny write to source systems | Critical | AI Governance. BI-022 AI operational execution prohibited | Preventive | Deny execution permission | Critical | AI Governance. BI-023 Forecast model validation | Governance | Reject unvalidated model in production | Critical | Model Risk. BI-024 Forecast uncertainty visible | Preventive | Require range/confidence display | High | BI Owner. BI-025 Legal hold overrides deletion | Preventive | Block deletion under hold | Critical | Legal. BI-026 Data retention enforcement | Preventive | Auto-purge per retention schedule | High | Data Governance. BI-027 Cross-border data restriction | Preventive | Block prohibited transfer | High | Legal/Security. BI-028 Pipeline failure escalation | Corrective | Escalate by severity | High | Platform. BI-029 Warehouse refresh monitoring | Detective | Alert on missed refresh | High | Platform. BI-030 Downstream impact notification | Corrective | Notify dependent dashboards/packages | High | Data Governance."
                            }
                        ]
